---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="交通指南 - 盐色运城" description="运城交通攻略——高铁、飞机、自驾、市内交通全方位指南。">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">交通指南</h1>
      <p class="text-stone max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">如何抵达运城，以及在运城如何出行</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- 高铁 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brick/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brick" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">高铁</h2>
        <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">运城北站是大西高铁上的重要站点。从太原约1.5小时，从西安约1小时，从北京约5小时可达。</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-stone">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            运城北站 — 市区约15公里
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            公交7路、14路直达市区
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            出租车约30元
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 飞机 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">飞机</h2>
        <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">运城关公机场（运城张孝机场）已开通北京、上海、广州、深圳、成都等国内主要城市航线。</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-stone">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            机场 — 市区约10公里
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            机场巴士 / 出租车约20元
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            飞行时间：北京约1.5小时
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 自驾 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-pool/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pool" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 17a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM19 17a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 16V6a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a1 1 0 00-1 1v10a1 1 0 001 1h1m8-1a1 1 0 01-1 1H9m4-1V8a1 1 0 011-1h2.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l3.414 3.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V16a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1m-6-1a1 1 0 001 1h1M5 17a2 2 0 104 0m-4 0a2 2 0 114 0m6 0a2 2 0 104 0m-4 0a2 2 0 114 0"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">自驾</h2>
        <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">运城高速公路网发达，G5京昆高速、G59呼北高速、S75侯平高速贯穿全境，自驾游览各景点最为方便。</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-stone">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            太原 — 运城约3.5小时
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            西安 — 运城约2.5小时
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
            洛阳 — 运城约2小时
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 市内交通 -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">市内交通</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-ink mb-2">公交车</h3>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed">运城公交线路覆盖市区主要景点，票价1-2元。可使用支付宝乘车码或办理运城公交卡。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-ink mb-2">出租车 / 网约车</h3>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed">出租车起步价6元/2公里，网约车滴滴、高德打车均可使用。前往周边县城建议包车或租车。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-ink mb-2">共享单车</h3>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed">市区内有哈啰、美团等共享单车，适合短途出行。盐湖周边有专门的自行车绿道，骑行体验极佳。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-salt-dark/10">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-ink mb-2">景区直通车</h3>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed">旅游旺季时，运城汽车站有发往主要景区的直通车，可直达关帝庙、永乐宫、鹳雀楼等热门目的地。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- 推荐路线 -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">推荐游览路线</h2>
      <p class="text-stone text-sm mb-8">根据你的时间，选择最合适的行程安排</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- 一日游 -->
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brick/5 to-transparent border border-brick/10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-brick text-white rounded-full text-xs font-bold">1日</span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-ink">经典一日游</h3>
          </div>
          <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-brick font-bold shrink-0">上午</span>
              <span class="text-stone">解州关帝庙 → 羊肉泡馍午餐</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-brick font-bold shrink-0">下午</span>
              <span class="text-stone">七彩盐湖景区 → 盐湖博物馆</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-brick font-bold shrink-0">傍晚</span>
              <span class="text-stone">盐湖观日落 → 市区晚餐</span>
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone/60 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-salt-dark/10">适合时间有限的过境游客</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 两日游 -->
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber/5 to-transparent border border-amber/10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber text-ink rounded-full text-xs font-bold">2日</span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-ink">深度两日游</h3>
          </div>
          <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-dark font-bold shrink-0">D1</span>
              <span class="text-stone">关帝庙 → 盐湖 → 鹳雀楼（住永济）</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-dark font-bold shrink-0">D2</span>
              <span class="text-stone">普救寺 → 黄河大铁牛 → 返程</span>
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone/60 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-salt-dark/10">覆盖运城西部精华景点</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 三日游 -->
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-pool/5 to-transparent border border-pool/10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-pool text-white rounded-full text-xs font-bold">3日</span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-ink">全景三日游</h3>
          </div>
          <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-pool font-bold shrink-0">D1</span>
              <span class="text-stone">关帝庙 → 盐湖 → 市区</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-pool font-bold shrink-0">D2</span>
              <span class="text-stone">永乐宫 → 广仁王庙 → 芮城</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-pool font-bold shrink-0">D3</span>
              <span class="text-stone">鹳雀楼 → 普救寺 → 返程</span>
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone/60 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-salt-dark/10">深度体验运城古建与自然之美</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
